\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs the baselining,
 forecasting,
 and threshold management of capacity and availability for all IT services and infrastructure administered by the Elko County Information Operations Department.
\end_layout

